{"tid":714723,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【大陸用字注意】忽悠","createTime":"2018-06-23T22:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T05:40:26.000Z","uid":69157,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"01252bdb13a6f3fe167230e452ee6d395d28339d","tid":714723,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T22:02:57.000Z","msg":"最近經常見到唔少人用忽悠呢個字，特別喺Youtube 留言，其實我哋香港都有類似用語，唔一定要借用東北用語<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><code>忽悠</code><br />\n<code>一詞來自東北方言，國語作糊弄或唬弄，其字面意思，是讓人陷於一種飄飄忽忽、神志不清、基本喪失判斷力的狀態。(取錄至wiki)</code></div><br />\n<br />\n香港方面，其實可用以上幾個詞語表達以上意思<br />\n例如：<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><code>撚化</code><br />\n<code>「撚化」指作弄，為六、七十年代常用詞。注意：此處之「撚」和「撚手」之撚同義，並不作粗口解。 (取錄至網典)</code> <br />\n<code>《說文》執也，《廣韻》以手撚物也，撚是個手部動作，大約指執、按、持取、搓揉。而「撚化」是指用手玩弄一物，玩到化境，喻為玩得非常精通之意，後來輾轉變成玩弄別人之意。(取錄至網上博文)</code></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<code>玩弄</code><br />\n<code>作弄</code><br />\n<code>戲弄</code><br />\n<code>把玩</code></div><br />\n以上都係常見且入文不失優雅嘅用字<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8347e2f826a6d35f0f889e513cd94ecb5a86abb2","tid":714723,"uid":179571,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T22:09:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26d9e596c5ef013087e8ff9e94bcf16ed40c2a0a","tid":714723,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T22:34:41.000Z","msg":"整蠱咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a2da45233b800c09ebf88739b8a5e74fde5d66","tid":714723,"uid":138489,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T22:39:35.000Z","msg":"老點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3de2371fecf9c05a6f7dc05d53df8f09953088","tid":714723,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T22:51:13.000Z","msg":"忽悠咁似fuckyou讀音<br />\n似係d支那人亂鳩咁改個解釋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.